This is Perl module DBIx::SimpleInfo.

INSTALLATION

Type the following command:

    $ curl -L http://cpanmin.us | perl - DBIx::SimpleInfo

Or install cpanm and then run the following command to install
DBIx::SimpleInfo:

    $ cpanm DBIx::SimpleInfo

If you get an archive of this distribution, unpack it and build it
as per the usual:

    $ tar xzf DBIx-SimpleInfo-$version.tar.gz
    $ cd DBIx-SimpleInfo-$version
    $ perl Makefile.PL
    $ make && make test

Then install it:

    $ make install

DOCUMENTATION

DBIx::SimpleInfo documentation is available as in POD. So you can do:

    $ perldoc DBIx::SimpleInfo

to read the documentation online with your favorite pager.

